<h2><none></h2>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-size:14px;">For the latest Mediterranean Update data on arrivals and fatalities please visit: <a href="http://migration.iom.int/europe">http://migration.iom.int/europe</a> #MigrationEurope</span></p>


</div>  </div><div class="item-1 item-even">  
